query:
SELECT DISTINCT component, componentType, location
FROM tmlReadings
WHERE LOWER(component) LIKE '%head%' 
   OR LOWER(componentType) LIKE '%head%'
   OR LOWER(location) LIKE '%head%'
   OR LOWER(component) LIKE '%north%'
   OR LOWER(component) LIKE '%south%'
   OR LOWER(location) LIKE '%north%'
   OR LOWER(location) LIKE '%south%'
LIMIT 50;
